metadata.description:
Viviane presents a proposal for separating behavior model columns from morphology model columns.

0:00 Introduction
00:08 Recap of Proposal of Separate Behavior Columns
11:41 Supporting Neuroscience
15:35 V1 as a Quick Relay to MT
22:21 Mapping the Neuroscience onto the Thousand Brains Theory
33:44 Benefits of this Approach
42:22 What Would this Mean in Monty?
